https://www.thivien.net/Khuy%E1%BA%BFt-danh-Vi%E1%BB%87t-Nam/author-kBTBt5Mbi6PPrH2sJkQAPw">Khuyết danh Việt Nam</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C3%B4-Ng%C3%B4n-Th%C3%B4ng/Th%E1%BB%8B-t%E1%BB%8Bch/poem-RPa636NjegP31Ruqigqdcg">Thị tịch - 示寂</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C3%B4-Ng%C3%B4n-Th%C3%B4ng/author-umEjhBNMswVyErICH_J1MQ">Vô Ngôn Thông</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%C3%AAn-K%E1%BA%BFt/Thung-L%C4%83ng-h%C3%A0nh/poem-p2nhZFT0UlZaSH48t6Kosw">Thung Lăng hành - 舂陵行</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%C3%AAn-K%E1%BA%BFt/author-9Y30zD24BFXrRqipoBvcFA">Nguyên Kết</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BA%ADu-Kh%E1%BA%A5u/V%C3%A3n-Ho%C3%A0-Th%C3%A2n-k%E1%BB%B3-1/poem-et9KlKexXTNBy4XwOT7YcA">Vãn Hoà Thân kỳ 1 - 挽和珅其一</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BA%ADu-Kh%E1%BA%A5u/author-svMQDOV_e4vEtYCGO8gq1g">Đậu Khấu</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
